data.name: editor.Text
data.value:
Select Ceil(Abs(2.15 + 2 * 3)) From dual;
Select ee.ID As "EmployeeID", ee.Name As "EmployeeName", tt.DeportmentName, ee.Gender As "EmployeeGender", ee.Weight As "EmployeeWeight", ee.Height As "EmployeeHeight", ee.BirthDay As "EmployeeBirthDay", ee.Address As "EmployeeAddress", ee.EMail As "EmployeeEMail" From Employee ee Left Join Deportment tt On (ee.DeportmentID = tt.DeportmentID) --This is a comment line... Where (1 = 1) Or ee.EmployeeID = '123456' Or (ee.Name Like 'Mar%' And ee.Gender = 'F' And ee.Address Is Not Null) Or (ee.Name Like 'Jo%' And ee.Gender = 'M' And ee.Address Is Not Null);
